{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/SynopsisS.png?t=1721186555\" /><br><br><i>MARGO - On the Brink</i> is a Turn-based RPG with roguelite/deckbuilding elements. Play as a nameless girl trapped deep inside the crumbling realities called &quot;The Brink&quot; and guide her to the truth of the sundered world. It will not be an easy journey as the hostile entities called &quot;Watchers&quot; are patrolling the ground. Draw strength from the benevolent beings called &quot;Whispers&quot; to stand up against the Watchers and find the long lost truth.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/GameplayS.png?t=1721186555\" /><br><br>In MARGO, resource management is critical. Instead of a traditional levelling system, progression is tied to the \u2018Whispers\u2019 in your party. Each Whisper has its own specialization, such as healing or defending in the form of program cards. The program cards are single-use spells/skills and have their own EXP/Level progression. The more you use them, the stronger they will become. Even after a \u2018Game Over,\u2019 the cards will slowly get stronger in every subsequence retry! Recruit all the Lost Whispers and collect all 100+ cards!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/Cards.gif?t=1721186555\" /><br><br>Dive into the ever-changing realities of the Brink and reach for the truth. Secrets and surprises await you in every randomized cycles as you journey deeper into the sundered world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/Dungeonsmol.gif?t=1721186555\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721186555","background_raw":"https://shared.akam